      <odd id="aspace_4789878fc432c6cc2f559858403c8b05">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 20-D (YRG 20-D), Records of committees of the Yale School of Art.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_f2206f42c9b7faf6ad67f8738c8ee006">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the School of Art, 1983.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
